    </section>

    <!-- Sources -->
    <section class="sources">
      <h2 class="section-h">Sources &amp; Further Reading</h2>
      <p>
        This article draws on reporting from <em>The Westerly Sun</em>, <em
          >The Providence Journal</em
        >, the National Register of Historic Places file on the Watch Hill
        Historic District, Craig Unger's biography of Rebekah Harkness, the
        See Westerly local history archive, and public records from the town
        of Westerly. Errors are mine — let us know and we'll fix them.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Related -->
    <section class="related">
      <h2 class="section-h">Keep Reading</h2>
      <div class="related-grid">
        <a
          href="/blog/best-things-to-do-in-watch-hill-ri"
